{"type": "article", "id": 3321, "title": "Nike & A.P.C. 联名 Free OG 运动鞋", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-06T08:02:47Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233019lvRdmzH31qhabJXf.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tNike 日前联手法国品牌 A.P.C. 推出了旗下 Free OG 鞋款的特别联名系列，鞋面的材质选用了高度耐磨的麂皮与网眼鞋面，去除了多余的细节处理与强烈的颜色对比，仅在鞋垫部分做了吉他与刀图案的十字交叉设计，搭配以平实干净的灰色、黑色与米色 3 种颜色的选择，延续了 A.P.C. 一直以来的低调风格。定价 150 欧元，<a href=\"http://www.apc.fr/wwuk/nike-td300.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233017rWy1quk0adXKO7EN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233017tAnxC5ZJX6uVU2v1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052330174WzAHNR6BsaJoFDL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233018f6ShNyG2gFv4br1w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}